〔 21 〕   参见王德新：《家事审判改革的理念革新与路径调适》，载《当代法学》2018 年第 1 期。
〔 22 〕   Webster v Norfolk County Council and the Children(By Their Children’s Guardian)[ 2009 ] EWCA Civ 59, [ 2009 ] 1 FLR
1378.
〔 23 〕   Regina v Secretary of State for the Home Department Ex Parte Simms[ 2000 ] 2 AC 115, 126.

